NAME
    Dpchrist::Module - utilities for Perl modules

DESCRIPTION
    This documentation describes module revision $Revision: 1.21 $.

    This is alpha test level software and may change or disappear at any
    time.

    This module includes:

    *   Additional functionality for Makefile.PL used by
        ExtUtils::MakeMaker.

    *   Standard test scripts.

INSTALLATION
        perl Makefile.PL
        make
        make test
        make install

DEPENDENCIES
        CPAN::Mini::Inject

SEE ALSO
        Dpchrist::Module::MakefilePL
        scripts in t/ directory

